{"tid":704849,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人記得《人類宇宙野史》？","createTime":"2018-06-16T15:53:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-17T01:26:23.000Z","uid":64894,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e77c6ce5a9fbf4dafaf752840d4fe82d7687667f","tid":704849,"uid":64894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T15:53:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=SY&amp;message=6483467&amp;highlight_id=0&amp;page=1&amp;authorOnly=False\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Ftype%3DSY%26message%3D6483467%26highlight_id%3D0%26page%3D1%26authorOnly%3DFalse&d=f24UGJmhnatya6gsXmPiZtWu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=3237522e\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=SY&amp;message=6483467&amp;highlight_id=0&amp;page=1&amp;authorOnly=False</a><br />\n<br />\n講故台至今最高質嘅科幻故，當初講到要出書、漫畫，點解最後又會冇晒聲氣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7872732e7876b2ac62315d636cf2e0684f732e8","tid":704849,"uid":8170,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T15:59:16.000Z","msg":"個開頭吹得太大，同埋係咁跳，收拾唔到"},{"pid":"d265597fb10f49311a6c2f2f82bfae4f241fa519","tid":704849,"uid":8170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T16:03:49.000Z","msg":"哈 我搵返我啲評論<br />\n<br />\n簡單少少分析下, 成個時序大概咁分: <br />\n1. 一開始係地球自己嘅科技故事, AI 到太空科技(星際飛行, 休眠等) <br />\n2. 之後科技進步到發現第二地球(未有人, 得野獸?) <br />\n3. 再過唔知幾多年再去, 發現塔星人, 發現神笛一族, 之後統治第二地球, 同塔星人共處 <br />\n4. 再過幾千年, 知道好多星系文明, 有交流, 有星盟 <br />\n5. 同淡藍文明, 塔星人進入黑洞(所謂嘅能量文明), 發現老人, 知道所謂宇宙係佢地文明(當佢叫神族先)嘅文明實驗品 <br />\n6. 知道神笛一族, 塔星人, 實驗之後, 知道埋宇宙要爆, 人類想救, 老人決定引爆 (完) <br />\n7. 倒返轉頭, 講爆之前(估計佢地黑洞內傾幾句計, 出面已經幾萬年?) 嘅人開始宗教狂熱 <br />\n8. 發現有平行宇宙(估計神族係3D嘅神, 而平行宇宙係4D嘅神造出嚟, 即係3D神族係4D神族嘅實驗品... <br />\n9. 可能而家第6宇宙條友會再重覆返 (5, 6) 啲 steps, 發現 4D神族老人家, 原來佢地實驗做咗幾萬個幾萬次方宇宙出嚟 <br />\n<br />\n至於會唔會一直 loop 5D神族, 6D神族, etc. 未知"},{"pid":"2d6d96a1dee65c252e78f050e4b7b21a97933b77","tid":704849,"uid":152665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T00:07:07.000Z","msg":"好似出左漫畫<br />\n<br />\n【兩登之光】90後寫《人類宇宙野史》 夥拍日本漫畫獎得主出書<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/194241/1?ref=android\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/194241/1?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\nLIHKG @ Android"},{"pid":"8ac87e789a636864a14b49c121dc950c2dc83dd6","tid":704849,"uid":541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T00:20:59.000Z","msg":"記得 個宇宙觀好撚正"},{"pid":"9b0d537b2d063b0d37a8618d94f43f69257b905e","tid":704849,"uid":541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T00:24:36.000Z","msg":"原來出左漫畫 邊到有得買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d891fe6ea4defb10425206236802a0797e1b378","tid":704849,"uid":64894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d6d96a1dee65c252e78f050e4b7b21a97933b77","tid":704849,"uid":152665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T00:07:07.000Z","msg":"好似出左漫畫<br />\n<br />\n【兩登之光】90後寫《人類宇宙野史》 夥拍日本漫畫獎得主出書<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/194241/1?ref=android\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/194241/1?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\nLIHKG @ Android"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T01:26:23.000Z","msg":"但我睇返最後好似冇出到"}]}